+modal('bip-alerts-email', "Email Alerts")
  p Designed and built the email delivery pipeline for the Alerts System.
  p Alerts were rendered as rich HTML emails with embedded timeseries charts — chart images were pre-rendered server-side via a Lambda-based chart renderer and attached to emails via Sendgrid.
  p The pipeline handled alert digests, notification scheduling, and per-user/per-org configuration.
  p Deployed a local playground for iterating on alert templates without needing production data.
